    <title>blog搭建问题总结</title>
    <link href="https://crankler.github.io/2018/06/20/blog-error/"/>
    <id>https://crankler.github.io/2018/06/20/blog-error/</id>
    <published>2018-06-20T10:43:16.000Z</published>
    <updated>2019-02-17T06:36:38.871Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="1-命名"><a href="#1-命名" class="headerlink" title="1.命名"></a>1.命名</h3><p>仓库名一定要和账号名相同（Repository.github.io ,注意这里的 Repository = Owner ）</p><p>###2.配置站点配置文件_config.yml<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">repository: git@github.com:sophiebob/sophiebob.github.io.git</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>记住不是<a href="http://git@github………………" target="_blank" rel="noopener">http://git@github………………</a></p><p>###3.搜索栏<br>默认的主题配置文件_config.yml是没有search，直接选择algolia_search/local_search 就会出现搜索栏<br>添加Algolia 搜索，注意是在站点配置文件中添加algolia配置信息<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">algolia:</span><br><span class="line">  applicationID: </span><br><span class="line">  apiKey: </span><br><span class="line">  adminApiKey: </span><br><span class="line">  indexName: <span class="comment">#创建index使用的Index Name</span></span><br><span class="line">  chunkSize: 5000</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>记得在环境变量中添加 HEXO_ALGOLIA_INDEXING_KEY<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ <span class="built_in">export</span> HEXO_ALGOLIA_INDEXING_KEY=粘贴上一步复制的 API KEY</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>之后执行 $ hexo algolia，显示出 info………… 说明正确</p><p>###4.更换新的文件夹（重新开始写博客）<br>重做系统或者删除相应的文件夹后会出现类似 fatal: Could not read from remote repository<br>并且会出些github帐号的更新确认<br>则重新设置public key和 SSH，并且确认GitHub账号即可</p><p>###5.写新的博客<br>新建一篇博客<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo new post <span class="string">"My New Post"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>More info: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/writing.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Writing</a></p><p>运行生成、部署命令<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo g   // 生成</span><br><span class="line">$ hexo d   // 部署</span><br><span class="line">$ hexo d -g <span class="comment">#在部署前先生成(相当于执行上俩个指令)</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>]]></content>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      github + hexo 博客搭建顺序与问题总结
    
    </summary>
    
